%% Diagram: Transactionally-staged job drain
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant API as API process
    participant DB as Postgres (ACID)
    participant ENQ as Enqueuer (drain)
    participant Q as Redis / Sidekiq
    participant W as Worker

    API->>DB: BEGIN
    API->>DB: INSERT ride
    API->>DB: INSERT staged_jobs(send_ride_receipt)
    API->>DB: COMMIT

    Note over DB: Both rows now visible<br/>to other transactions

    loop every poll interval
        ENQ->>DB: BEGIN (REPEATABLE READ)
        ENQ->>DB: SELECT ... FROM staged_jobs LIMIT N
        ENQ->>Q: ENQUEUE jobs
        ENQ->>DB: DELETE selected staged_jobs
        ENQ->>DB: COMMIT
    end

    Q-->>W: dequeue job
    W->>W: send receipt email
